  "title": "SALES MANAGER",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>You will lead the store’s sales performance by managing the sales team and delivering an excellent customer experience. This role drives revenue growth through implementing effective sales strategies, overseeing daily retail operations, and developing staff to maximize productivity and profitability.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Drive store sales performance by executing targeted sales initiatives to achieve revenue goals</li><li>Lead and manage the sales team to enhance their effectiveness and meet performance objectives</li><li>Deliver an excellent customer experience by monitoring service quality and resolving issues promptly</li><li>Implement sales strategies that align with business objectives and market trends to increase sales</li><li>Oversee daily retail operations to ensure smooth functioning and operational efficiency</li><li>Develop staff capabilities through coaching and training to maximize team productivity and profitability</li></ul>",
